net.opentsdb.core

类 HistogramRowSeq

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.HistogramRowSeq
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Iterable<HistogramDataPoint>, HistogramDataPoints, iHistogramRowSeq

    public class HistogramRowSeq
extends Object
implements iHistogramRowSeq
    Represents a read-only sequence of continuous HBase rows.

    This class stores in memory the data of one or more continuous HBase rows for a given time series. To consolidate memory, the data points are stored in two byte arrays: one for the time offsets/flags and another for the values. Access is granted via pointers.

    从以下版本开始:
    3.0

      • getAggregatedTags

        public List<String> getAggregatedTags()
        从接口复制的说明: HistogramDataPoints
        Returns the tags associated with some but not all of the data points.

        When this instance represents the aggregation of multiple time series (same metric but different tags), HistogramDataPoints.getTags() returns the tags that are common to all data points (intersection set) whereas this method returns all the tags names that are not common to all data points (union set minus the intersection set, also called the symmetric difference).

        If this instance does not represent an aggregation of multiple time series, the list returned is empty.

        指定者:
        getAggregatedTags 在接口中 HistogramDataPoints
        返回:
        A non-null list of tag names.

      • aggregatedSize

        public int aggregatedSize()
        从接口复制的说明: HistogramDataPoints
        Returns the number of data points aggregated in this instance.

        When this instance represents the aggregation of multiple time series (same metric but different tags), HistogramDataPoints.size() returns the number of data points after aggregation, whereas this method returns the number of data points before aggregation.

        If this instance does not represent an aggregation of multiple time series, then 0 is returned.

        指定者:
        aggregatedSize 在接口中 HistogramDataPoints
        返回:
        A positive integer.

      • iterator

        public HistogramSeekableView iterator()
        从接口复制的说明: HistogramDataPoints
        Returns a zero-copy view to go through size() data points.

        The iterator returned must return each DataPoint in O(1). The DataPoint returned must not be stored and gets invalidated as soon as next is called on the iterator. If you want to store individual data points, you need to copy the timestamp and value out of each DataPoint into your own data structures.

        指定者:
        iterator 在接口中 Iterable<HistogramDataPoint>
        指定者:
        iterator 在接口中 HistogramDataPoints
        返回:
        An iterator over the data points.

      • timestamp

        public long timestamp(int i)
        从接口复制的说明: HistogramDataPoints
        Returns the timestamp associated with the ith data point. The first data point has index 0.

        This method must be implemented in O(HistogramDataPoints.aggregatedSize()) or better.

        It is guaranteed that 

        timestamp(i) < timestamp(i+1)
        指定者:
        timestamp 在接口中 HistogramDataPoints
        参数:
        i - The index to fetch a timestamp for
        返回:
        A strictly positive integer.
